00:33:38,080 --> 00:33:41,470
Anggota keluargaku mati-matian
berusaha menutupi fakta itu,

456
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:48,070
tapi aku memberi tahu orang lain.

457
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:01,930
Itu pasti sulit bagimu.

458
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:04,130
Bukan aku.

459
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,120
Tapi kakakku.

460
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,280
Dia pasti lebih menderita.

461
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:21,460
Tapi aku benar-benar tidak tahu

462
00:34:23,929 --> 00:34:25,909
dan hanya mengeluh tentang rasa sakitku.

463
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:40,120
Soo-hyun.

464
00:34:41,699 --> 00:34:42,719
Ya?

465
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,040
Aku harus bagaimana?

466
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:14,880
Putra ketiga Grup Kisung
membuat keributan.

467
00:35:15,850 --> 00:35:18,090
Lihat? Mereka gagal mengawasi putra mereka

